title: Lombardi's Week 2 Reactions | GM Street (Ep. 303)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Mitchell Trubisky's 'Monday Night Football' performance, Seattle's struggles, and Week 2 standouts, and then give out awards for who stole the show this weekend.
